column5: I am heading to Lake simcoe on Saturday going out from Innisfil. How is the ice, can it handle a ATV or sled over to the Islands? I know we have had lots of snow latley and probably is slushy, any info would be great.  Thanks
Lots of sleds going out from Innisfil...and lots of slush!  From what I've been hearing, fewer and fewer ATV's...
slushy areas out of Shanty Bay 12" of good ice . TB
